Projects

3D Printed Base

A 3D printing version of the intial indicator base. Slight tweaks were made to the design to conserve printing material.

CNC Turret

A simple model of a tool setup of a specific CNC turret. It was used as a visiual aid for easy tool setup.

Die Holder

This holder secures the pin cleaner to a rotating shaft. As the pin cleaner is rotating, it is able to clean the cable.

Indicator Base

A base to hold a cable connector as a pressure gage is used to measure specific points. This is the final design of the base. It was originally designed to be handheld but was later altered to be stationary.

Indicator Base (Initial)

A base used to secure and stablize a cable as it undergoes quality control inspection. This is the initial design for handheld use.

Pin Cleaner

This part removes debris and residues that are lodged in a cable after it is cut and processed.

Wrapping Clamp

A clamp to hold a bundle of cables as it is prepped. This is used to lessen the strain on worker's arms.
